            El envío de devolución corre por cuenta del cliente.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="politica-cambios-page__shipping-card politica-cambios-page__shipping-card--orange">
          <div class="politica-cambios-page__shipping-header">
            <svg class="politica-cambios-page__shipping-icon" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <line x1="16.5" y1="9.4" x2="7.5" y2="4.21"></line>
              <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"></path>
